# Keep the build context small + secret-free. Cargo fetches cggmp24/bsv-rs from
# the network during the build, so only the workspace SOURCE is needed here.
.git
target
**/target
node_modules
**/node_modules
.wrangler
**/.wrangler
graphify-out
# SECURITY: never ship secrets into the image/context.
secrets.md
**/secrets.md
*.log
